        </div>
        <p class="text-blue-100 mb-6">
          Professional architectural and engineering services for your ideal living space. We offer ADU design, structural engineering, and home renovation services.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a href="#" class="p-2 border border-blue-400/20 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600/20">
            <span class="sr-only">Twitter</span>
